  "text": "Remark 16. Reference [CITATION_1] considered the problem of exponential 1 output tracking control for positive switched linear systems with ADT, which focuses on the asymptotic stability and the exponential 1 performance index. There are some differences between [CITATION_2] and this paper. Firstly, the finite-time stability in this paper and the asymptotic stability in [CITATION_3] are two absolutely different concepts. Secondly, the performance indexes are also different. Finally, this paper uses MDADT approach instead of ADT method in [CITATION_4] . So we do not compare the simulation results.",
